        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-03-22 14:11:58.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nthank you. \n\nPlease let me know why you are sure we can delete RequestContext.java. in APPC, we have directed graph which would directly use java class. did you verify that as well?",
        "patchset_number": 3
